Feign death does not always work. If you get the message [Your name] has fallen to the ground, it means your FD failed and the mob can still see you.  You will need to hit stand and continue the battle or try FD again (though, usually, an FD failure results in death if you waited to use it until you really needed it). At higher levels, it gets better after you obtain Death Peace. I probably get 1 failure out of 20 (that number may be optimistic, but it seems right to me).

